div.div: Plots for values of each socioeconomic indicator (y-axis) through time (x-axis).
div.p: Red and blue correspond to before and after the implementation of the reserve, respectively. This figure contains information for total landings (a), total income (b), lobster landings (c), urchin landings (d), snail landings (e), sea cucumber landings (f), lobster income (g), urchin income (h), snail income (i), and sea cucumber income (j).
